<details class="group bg-surface-container p-6 cursor-pointer"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-on-surface">How much does a consultation cost?<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform">add</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Initial consultations at Flake & Flake are complimentary. We'll discuss your situation, evaluate your options, and give you an honest assessment — no obligation.</p></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container p-6 cursor-pointer"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-on-surface">What areas of law do you practice?<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform">add</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">We practice estate planning, probate, personal injury, medical malpractice, FTCA/VA malpractice, business law, and contract law. See our practice areas page for details.</p></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container p-6 cursor-pointer"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-on-surface">Do you handle cases outside of Henderson?<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform">add</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Yes. While our office is in Henderson, we serve clients throughout Las Vegas, Southern Nevada, and for federal cases, nationwide.</p></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container p-6 cursor-pointer"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-on-surface">How do personal injury fees work?<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform">add</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Personal injury and medical malpractice cases are handled on a contingency fee basis — you pay nothing unless we recover compensation for you.</p></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container p-6 cursor-pointer"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-on-surface">How do estate planning fees work?<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform">add</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Estate planning services are billed at a flat fee, quoted after your initial consultation. We provide transparent pricing with no hidden costs.</p></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container p-6 cursor-pointer"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold text-on-surface">What should I bring to my consultation?<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform">add</span></summary><p class="mt-4 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Bring any relevant documents — existing estate plans, medical records, accident reports, contracts, or correspondence related to your matter. Don't worry if you don't have everything; we'll guide you.</p></details>
